These are Puzzles for 6x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, sprite
There are 2 different favourite colors: turquise, chestnut
There are 2 different nationalities: japanese, russian
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: sunflower, poppy
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, time-travel
2 different pets are kept: goldfish, horse
1. the russian is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
2. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
3. the person drinking fanta is the person who likes chestnut##1
4. the person drinking sprite is in an even position##4
5. the person who growspoppy is the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |
| Beverage      | fanta   | sprite        |
| Color          | chestnut    | turquise     |
| Nationality         | russian | japanese   |
| Flower           | sunflower  | poppy |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy   | time-travel       |
| Pet           | horse   | goldfish      |

