.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, tea
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: crime, animation
The people have 2 different hobbies: video-games, writing
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, vegafina
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: iris, aconite
There are 2 different favourite colors: light-blue, fuchsia
1. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
2. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the vegafina-smoker##3
3. the person drinking juice is in an odd position##4
4. the person watching animation movies is the person who's hobby is writing##1
5. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Beverage      | juice       | tea      |
| Movie-Genre          | crime   | animation |
| Hobby         | video-games | writing  |
| Cigar   | vegafina        | alhambra     |
| Flower   | iris       | aconite   |
| Color           | light-blue        | fuchsia |

