.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-4-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: june, may
The people have 2 different jobs:  fisherman, architect
There are 2 different nationalities: german, pakistani
There 2 different types of food: pear, lime
2 different pets are kept: mouse, goat
1. the owner of the goat is in an odd position##4
2. the pakistani is on the left of the architect##1
3. the architect is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
4. the architect is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person eating pear##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |
| Beverage      | cola      | fanta   |
| Birthday         | june | may |
| Job   | fisherman   | architect    |
| Nationality   | pakistani | german  |
| Food         | pear      | lime  |
| Pet     | goat    | mouse     |

